<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>79</hymn_number>
<title>Msalaba Wa Aibu TZR79</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Msalaba wa aibu,
 Ulinipa amani;
 Uliniondoa kifungoni,
 Nilimotesekea.

[V2]
 Ee, Mwokozi wangu, Yesu
 Nitamwendea nani?
 Najiweka msalabani,
 Nikaoshwe damuni.

[V3]
 Nakupenda Bwana Yesu,
 Kwa kunipenda kwako,
 Napendezwa nikutumikie
 Maisha yangu yote.

[V4]
 Usifiwe Bwana Yesu,
 Kwa ulivyonifia,
 Aleluya, nakushukuru,
 Uliyenikomboa.

[V5]
 Msalaba ulishinda
 Nguvu zake adui,
 Ili mimi nikombolewe,
 Niwe mwana wa Mungu.</lyrics>
</song>